The superstar who currently is enjoying the beautiful after-events of his successful show, Starboy Fest, at the O2 over the weekend was in the midst of his guys earlier today and he revealed contrary to popular beliefs by people that Nigerian artistes don’t show love to each other, they are all actually cool and always wish each other well. He revealed though there might be a misunderstanding between on or two or more artistes, they still wish they all win and conquer in all their endeavours. You all would recall Wizkid invited almost the whole Nigerian music industry artistes to perform at his concert in London, uniting the culture. Watch video below:   A post shared by GoldMyne TV (@goldmynetv) on Oct 22, 2019 at 7:38am PDT //www.instagram.com/embed.js The post Though We Might Have Our Differences, But We Love One Another – Watch Wizkid Speaks On Unity Amongst Nigerian Artistes appeared first on tooXclusive. Source: Too Xclusive